author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Who will finish with a better record: Knicks or Nets?
text:
Nathaniel S. Butler/NBAE/Getty Images The Knicks and Nets enter another season to compete to be the best team in New York. The Knicks and the Nets each have a set of challenges to face this NBA season - but many wonder which team will be better.
Both of the city's NBA teams have struggled to be relevant in a weak Eastern Conference in the past couple of seasons - and will both likely be in the hunt for the eighth seed this year to sneak into the playoffs.
The Knicks made some key additions this offseason as they look to improve on last season's pathetic 17-65 record.
